      "name": "Bench-top hemolysis validation — FDA pump loop",
      "description": "Predicted normalised index of hemolysis (NIH) compared against in-vitro measurements from the FDA generic pump loop at five flow-speed operating points (2 L/min 2500 RPM, 3 L/min 2500 RPM, 4 L/min 3000 RPM, 5 L/min 3500 RPM, 6 L/min 4000 RPM). Mean absolute error 8.3%; all predictions within experimental uncertainty bands. Test protocol specified pump settings entered by trained laboratory technician following a fixed script; no off-nominal input conditions were evaluated."
