    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Seven of thirteen credibility factors assessed at or above required level for MRL 2. Six factors not assessed are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 4. The use-error factor was not assessed; however, the assessment team concluded that laboratory-controlled validation conditions and the structured clinical perfusionist training programme provide sufficient operational safeguards for the CPB indication. Overall credibility is judged sufficient to support regulatory submission for the Class II CPB device.",
